>\n激進派通常堅持己見，好少和解團結呢樣果樣</blockquote><br />\n滅又滅唔到，再鬥又冇得益，點解唔和？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇架喎，睇社記人力熱狗咁多年就知<br />\n唔係咁既性格就入左泛民啦，條路易行好多<br />\n總之佢地冇叫過人和解啦"},{"pid":"dc917066881bee3fe6542637fb8e27c8fedb063a","tid":20392,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢幾時叫人和解？<br />\n激進派通常堅持己見，好少和解團結呢樣果樣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n熱狗咪又係搞埋d和理非遊行 有幾激??</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n和解係我叫你地兩邊啲支持者嘅<br />\nBtw 熱血時報同熱血公民分開咗<br />\n方舟講嘢 唔好入松泰"},{"pid":"d11c663cd453e2948821bab3ef165fe23dd95c1f","tid":20392,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黃洋達究竟憎本民青d咩？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n憎本民青推左陳澤滔出黎搞到佢又輸掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最衰陳澤滔啦, 走黎界佢票</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一日最衰都係陳澤滔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD票明明寫住係蝗上既仲黎搶票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6312d3b8e1b6ca0904adc32169f684ace5b12cbe","tid":20392,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:18:51.000Z","msg":"好撚煩"},{"pid":"ef8d576c9eaae9dba99aa1d30751ea60565751fb","tid":20392,"uid":11830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:19:00.000Z","msg":"都未講黃洋達個所謂59條罪根本無告"},{"pid":"bd691c80bfa846bdda0983336c0be7d40a329427","tid":20392,"uid":1494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T11:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢老婆先難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過算啦 其實ed野得我地會留意<br />\n試下出去同人講咩皇上皇后堂主神驅咁 <br />\n根本無人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n要和解一定係要更加大既共同敵人出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc8773551a293bdce65d41b373da1bcd50d9e99","tid":20392,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi